The '''flag of Amman''' is the flag of the city and municipality of [[Amman]], [[Jordan]].<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Amman-Jordan-20x30cm-8x12in-Diplomat-Flags/dp/B00DRLOJ2Y | title=Amman Jordan Flag 20x30cm – 8x12in for Diplomat-Flags Car Flag Poles | website=[[Amazon.com]] | accessdate=3 March 2016 }}</ref> It is officially recognized by the Jordanian government.{{fact|date=March 2016}} The foreground shows the word Amman written in Arabic in the Amman serif font, and in the background hills and houses. this flag had been adopted by the greater municipality of Amman in 2009 instead of the old "Arch flag".

